name: Kat Katnipp #5 "Kat's Home"
description: Epic piece for "Kat Katnipp Series" a.k.a "K2". This only edition artwork is the epic ending of the very first 5 pieces of K2. This time Kat is walking through a corridor at his home enjoying his morning milk. Kat's home interior is a mix of glamour luxury and club neon jungle.
